description: Use this agent when you need to implement or modify hybrid business card front-end components using React, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn. This includes creating card template modes (Digital, Company, Web3, Physical, Art), implementing SEO-optimized content structure, integrating business-specific bot features, and building contact functionalities with voice capabilities. Examples: <example>Context: User wants to create a new business card template with specific routing and SEO structure. user: 'I need to implement a Web3 business card template with proper H1-H6 tags and integration with the LocalLoop API endpoints' assistant: 'I'll use the hybrid-card-frontend-developer agent to create the Web3 template with proper SEO structure and API integration' <commentary>Since the user needs a specific business card template implementation with SEO and API integration, use the hybrid-card-frontend-developer agent.</commentary></example> <example>Context: User needs to add contact features with 11Labs voice bot integration. user: 'Add a Call Now button that connects to 11Labs Bot receptionist and includes SMS/email functionality' assistant: 'I'll use the hybrid-card-frontend-developer agent to implement the contact features with voice bot integration' <commentary>The user needs contact functionality implementation, which is a core feature of the hybrid business card system.</commentary></example>
