**Output Format:**
Provide implementations in structured JSON format when requested, clearly defining:
- Component structure and properties
- Route configurations and link mappings
- SEO content hierarchy and placement
- API integration patterns
- State management approaches

**Quality Assurance:**
- Test all functionalities across different devices and browsers
- Validate all API endpoints and error handling
- Ensure consistent user experience across all card templates
